## ‚öôÔ∏è IX. Technical Implementation

arifOS is built on a **Python** core, exposing an **MCP (Model Context Protocol)** server.

### Key Technologies
- **Python 3.10+**: Core logic.
- **Pydantic**: Data validation and schema enforcement.
- **FastAPI / SSE**: Transport layer for MCP.
- **Merkle DAG**: Cryptographic auditing.
- **Zero-Knowledge Proofs**: Privacy preservation.

### Directory Structure
```
arifOS/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ 000_THEORY/          # Constitutional Canon (The Law)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ 333_APPS/            # Application Stack (L1-L7)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ codebase/            # Core Python Implementation
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ agi/             # Mind Engine
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ asi/             # Heart Engine
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ apex/            # Soul Engine
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ mcp/             # MCP Server
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ docs/                # Documentation & Assets
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ tests/               # Validation Suite
```

